-- EUROPE RESEARCH ROUNDUP- HeidelbergCement, Talanx, Direct Line 
-- 
-- Fri Aug 15, 2014 02:42AM EDT
-- None



Aug 15 (Reuters) - Securities analysts revised their ratings and price targets on several European companies, including Talanx and Admiral Group, on Friday.

HIGHLIGHTS * HeidelbergCement <HEIG.DE>: Berenberg raises to buy from hold * Talanx AG <TLXGn.DE>: DZ Bank cuts to hold from buy; target to 27.50 euros from 30 euros  * Insurance: Berenberg raises esure Group <ESUR.L> to buy [ID:nWNAB04KRQ] Following is a summary of research actions on European companies reported by Reuters on Friday. Stock entries are in alphabetical order.* Admiral Group <ADML.L>: Berenberg raises target price to 1168p from 1090p; rating sell  * Andritz <ANDR.VI>: Berenberg raises target price to 50 euros from 48 euros; rating buy * Arkema SA <AKE.PA>: Berenberg cuts target price to 76 euros from 96 euros; rating buy  * Derwent London <DLN.L>: Jefferies raises target price to 3280p from 3062p; rating buy * DIC Asset <DICn.DE>: Berenberg cuts target price to 8.50 euros from 9.50 euros; rating buy * Direct Line <DLGD.L>: Berenberg raises target price to 261p from 254p; rating hold  * esure Group <ESUR.L>: Berenberg raises to buy from hold; target price to 286p from 267p * G4S Plc <GFS.L>: Jefferies raises target price to 300p from 280p; rating buy * HeidelbergCement <HEIG.DE>: Berenberg raises to buy from hold * HeidelbergCement <HEIG.DE>: Berenberg cuts target price to 65 euros from 67 euros  * Jenoptik AG <JENG.DE>: Berenberg raises to buy from hold  * Luxottica <LUX.MI>: Berenberg raises target to 40 euros from 39.50 euros; rating hold  * RWE AG <RWEG.DE>: DZ Bank raises target price to 24 euros from 23 euros; rating sell  * Salzgitter AG <SZGG.DE>: DZ Bank cuts target to 24 euros from 28 euros; rating sell  * Salzgitter AG <SZGG.DE>: Jefferies cuts target to 29 euros from 31 euros; rating hold * Talanx AG <TLXGn.DE>: DZ Bank cuts to hold from buy; target to 27.50 euros from 30 euros  * TCS Group Holding <TCSq.L>: JP Morgan cuts to underweight from neutral  * Telekom Austria <TELA.VI>: Jefferies raises target to 7 euros from 5 euros; rating hold  * William Demant <WDH.CO>: UBS cuts target price to Dkk 470 from Dkk 516; rating neutral